But he heard in the middle of the night, the Spirit of the Lord told him, "I want you to take your tent, take it down, put it in the back of those semis and get out of here quick.

01:38:50.539 --> 01:38:59.373
" Well, he told all the people the next day, "I'm sorry, we're canceling the meeting.

01:39:06.205 --> 01:39:06.503
The Lord said to take down the tent and pack it up and get out of here quick.

01:39:17.190 --> 01:39:17.580
" And the pastors and the people around there said, "Well, you're not hearing God.

01:39:17.580 --> 01:39:22.419
Why would God say to do that?

01:39:22.419 --> 01:39:28.230
There's so many people getting born again.

01:39:28.230 --> 01:39:32.420
There's so many people getting healed.

01:39:32.420 --> 01:39:34.890
You're missing it, brother.

01:39:48.680 --> 01:39:48.960
" And Jack said, "I'm sorry.

01:39:49.240 --> 01:39:51.676
I have an urgency.

01:39:51.676 --> 01:39:55.120
We must take the tent down.

01:40:14.250 --> 01:40:14.800
" And all the other believers around there saying, "You're hearing the devil.

01:40:40.080 --> 01:40:40.444
That's you.

01:40:40.444 --> 01:40:42.267
Just take your authority.

01:40:42.267 --> 01:40:44.027
Just take your authority, Jack.

01:40:44.027 --> 01:40:45.360
Everything's going to be okay.

01:40:45.360 --> 01:40:54.120
That's just the devil trying to run you out of here.

01:41:02.760 --> 01:41:03.100
" He said, "Well, you say what you want to, but I'm taking my tent down.

01:41:03.100 --> 01:41:15.760
" So he took the tent down, and all of a sudden, the levees, the dike, the bridge, the dam broke in that valley.

01:41:15.760 --> 01:41:23.462
And in just a matter of minutes, he had 40 men lifting up that tent and putting it in there.

01:41:25.371 --> 01:41:26.880
They were trying to flee and get away.

01:41:29.143 --> 01:41:29.771
And he said, "Please don't leave me.

01:41:29.771 --> 01:41:32.097
Help me put my tent inside of the truck.

01:41:32.097 --> 01:41:39.707
" So those 40 men lifted that up there and they got out just in time.

01:41:53.209 --> 01:41:53.560
He said he was looking in the rearview mirror, and where he was was completely flooded and destroyed.

01:41:58.080 --> 01:42:12.709
And if he would have been there, he would have lost his tent and all those people that were in that revival would have died.

01:42:21.648 --> 01:42:22.496
They would have drowned.

01:42:29.560 --> 01:42:30.139
The people that stayed and did not listen drowned.

01:42:30.139 --> 01:42:32.360
Churches were washed out.

01:42:32.360 --> 01:42:34.773
People died by the thousands.

01:42:35.933 --> 01:42:41.920
And so I just want to let you know, you say, "Well, that's torment, that's whatever.

01:42:41.920 --> 01:42:44.853
" You take your authority.

01:42:44.853 --> 01:42:50.693
Jack Coe, he was a man, a mighty man of God.

01:42:50.693 --> 01:42:58.289
And I'm just saying, don't get flaky.

01:42:58.289 --> 01:43:04.155
Don't be in presumption.

01:43:04.155 --> 01:43:08.099
Hear Him and hear Him again.

01:43:08.099 --> 01:43:13.942
Listen to the voice of God and He'll protect you.

01:43:13.942 --> 01:43:15.119
Don't take that flight.

01:43:15.119 --> 01:43:19.280
Don't drive down that road.

01:43:19.280 --> 01:43:20.820
Listen to Him and listen again.

01:43:20.820 --> 01:43:22.729
Don't go to that event.

01:43:31.378 --> 01:43:39.176
I just try to tell you this because I hear a lot of people get real flaky with stuff, and we've got to stay grounded and stay in the Word and don't just be listening to all kinds of voices.

01:43:39.176 --> 01:43:42.420
Listen to one voice: the Holy Spirit.

01:44:02.680 --> 01:44:02.980
But the people I hear, they email us and say, "Well, you know, I hear an audible voice talk to me all the time" and all this stuff.

01:44:02.980 --> 01:44:15.760
I'm going to tell you, you know how many times Brandon has heard an audible voice of the Spirit of God talking to him—I'm talking about an audible voice?

01:44:15.760 --> 01:44:18.207
Never.

01:44:18.207 --> 01:44:22.000
In fact, well, I'd say once.

01:44:22.000 --> 01:44:26.460
I've heard it one time.

01:44:54.159 --> 01:44:54.895
But out of all the time I've been born again, I never hear an audible voice.

01:44:54.895 --> 01:45:04.053
The Lord does not talk to me in an audible voice.

01:45:07.119 --> 01:45:13.040
He talks to me in the still, small voice on the inside of me.

01:45:20.159 --> 01:45:21.222
And the more you pay attention to the still, small voice, that still, small voice gets loud.

01:45:26.719 --> 01:45:29.299
And it's no longer still and small to me; it's loud.

01:45:44.577 --> 01:45:48.035
I hear Him like I'm hearing you.

01:45:59.547 --> 01:45:59.884
He talks to me and we talk all the time.

01:46:02.560 --> 01:46:10.639
He will talk all the time to you.

01:46:14.160 --> 01:46:14.880
He has an opinion about everything.

01:46:22.366 --> 01:46:22.697
The Holy Spirit has an opinion about everything.

01:46:22.697 --> 01:46:31.226
But the more you have a relationship with Him, the more He will become real to you.

01:46:52.239 --> 01:47:19.958
When you get real with God, God will become real to you.

01:47:34.639 --> 01:47:34.989
And He will talk to you in the still, small voice inside of you.

01:47:34.989 --> 01:47:41.540
It's not weird, you know, "Oh, I hear voices out here.

01:47:41.540 --> 01:47:43.659
" Those are devils.

01:47:43.659 --> 01:47:44.719
99.

01:47:44.719 --> 01:47:52.411
9% of the time, I can probably guarantee you, you're listening to demonic spirits.

01:47:52.411 --> 01:48:00.533
He's the still, small voice inside of you, and He'll talk to you through His Word.

01:48:00.533 --> 01:48:03.223
Get in this Bible and read it.

01:48:04.426 --> 01:48:10.555
And the more you read it, I'm telling you, it's an enlightenment.

01:48:13.737 --> 01:48:14.880
The eyes of your understanding will be enlightened.

01:48:15.720 --> 01:48:19.220
The Bible's a lamp unto my feet and a light unto my path.

01:48:26.920 --> 01:48:27.180
I will hide the Word in my heart that I might not sin against Him.

01:48:27.180 --> 01:48:32.533
So, get that Word down inside of you and pray and pray some more and fast.

01:48:32.533 --> 01:48:35.960
If you say, "Well, I don't hear God," fast a little bit.

01:48:35.960 --> 01:48:37.260
Make your flesh squirm.

01:48:37.260 --> 01:48:41.160
Read your Bible, pray, and you'll hear Him.

01:48:41.160 --> 01:48:44.103
Practice His presence.

01:48:44.103 --> 01:48:46.770
Practice the Father's presence.

01:48:46.770 --> 01:48:47.930
I practice it.

01:48:54.800 --> 01:49:04.620
I talk to Him just like I'm talking to Braden right there.

01:49:14.088 --> 01:49:14.346
I talk to Him.

01:49:45.800 --> 01:49:46.080
My kids know I don't act all hyperspiritual and all weird and hermeneutical or theosophical.

01:49:46.080 --> 01:49:52.044
I'm just an old country guy who has been raised in a Christian home.

01:50:00.100 --> 01:50:00.350
You have to be hungry for it and you have to be thirsty.

01:50:29.319 --> 01:50:29.519
And He said, "Those that knock, He will open the door.

01:50:29.519 --> 01:50:31.786
Those that thirst, He will give you a drink.

01:50:31.786 --> 01:50:33.119
" Remember, you're pursuing Him.

01:50:33.119 --> 01:50:36.240
How desperate are you for change?

01:50:36.240 --> 01:50:40.223
How thirsty, how hungry are you for change in your life?

01:50:40.223 --> 01:50:53.281
"Blessed are the pure in heart, for they will see God.

01:50:53.281 --> 01:50:55.880
" That's Jesus.

01:51:09.840 --> 01:51:10.090
But I just want to give you an encouraging word today.

01:51:10.090 --> 01:51:15.818
Thank you for helping me pray this morning.

01:51:59.760 --> 01:51:59.946
I appreciate every single one of you for always being a part of this and coming and taking it seriously.

01:52:22.239 --> 01:52:22.600
I don't take it for granted ever that anyone would come and pray with me and just be a part of our prayer channel.

01:52:22.600 --> 01:52:24.240
We're growing every day.

01:52:24.240 --> 01:52:41.939
We're almost to 570,000 people, and we're so grateful for every single one of you that subscribe and are a part of this prayer channel.

01:52:41.939 --> 01:52:57.189
We have been praying for a million, and I believe the power of prayer changes things.

01:52:57.199 --> 01:53:07.170
We didn't realize Diana said, "Isn't it so neat that Kathryn Kuhlman named her whole organization Prayer Changes Things?

01:53:07.170 --> 01:53:12.213
" We didn't know when we named ours Prayer Changes Things; that was just leading by the Holy Spirit.

01:53:16.480 --> 01:53:21.840
And I said, because it's somebody we admire, I said, "That is wonderful, Diana.

01:53:21.840 --> 01:53:33.359
Look what the Lord did, even when we didn't know what He was doing—just following the leading of the Holy Spirit inside of you.

01:53:33.359 --> 01:53:35.840
" He has such great plans for every single one of you.

01:53:35.840 --> 01:53:39.097
He loves every single one of you so much.

01:53:39.097 --> 01:53:40.907
And He's coming.

01:53:40.907 --> 01:53:44.336
Do you know Jesus is coming?

01:54:06.719 --> 01:54:06.999
He's standing at the door, ladies and gentlemen.

01:54:08.400 --> 01:54:09.290
He's coming, but He's wanting a harvest.

01:54:13.480 --> 01:54:16.583
He's leaving the ninety-nine to go after the one right now.

01:54:16.583 --> 01:54:20.046
So you pray.

01:54:25.599 --> 01:54:29.200
And like Sister Billye said last night, she talked about interceding for the unsaved.

01:54:33.600 --> 01:55:06.819
And you'll be surprised when you get over there who made it because of your prayers—interceding for your cousins, for your aunts, for your uncles, for your grandmas, for your grandpas, for your moms, your dads, your wife, your children.

01:55:06.819 --> 01:55:18.009
You're going to be—it's going to be—I'm telling you, He said that He wished that none should perish, but all come to repentance.

01:55:18.887 --> 01:55:26.011
And I believe that today your unsaved loved ones are going to have an experience with God.

01:55:26.011 --> 01:55:30.719
So, just have an expectation for it.

01:55:30.719 --> 01:55:32.544
It's time.

01:55:32.544 --> 01:55:37.560
We're going to start to see the greatest harvest of souls this world has ever seen.

01:55:37.560 --> 01:55:44.591
Billy Graham, what he did is nothing compared to what we're about to see, and he did a lot—his tent meetings and his things.

01:55:44.591 --> 01:55:51.875
I believe that what we're about to see is going to be like, "Wow," you know?

01:55:51.875 --> 01:55:53.496
It's time to believe God for bigger.

01:55:53.496 --> 01:55:55.760
So, God bless you all.

01:56:06.570 --> 01:56:06.740
I think that's good today for right now.

01:56:10.880 --> 01:56:11.040
I might come on this evening; depends on what I'm feeling this afternoon.

01:56:11.040 --> 01:56:15.664
But I wanted to say, I don't know if it's really a happy Yom Kippur.

01:56:31.567 --> 01:56:33.430
I don't even know if it's, you know, I know it's the Day of Repentance, a Day of Atonement, right?

01:56:33.440 --> 01:56:45.906
So glory to God for His mercy that we have Him now.

01:56:45.906 --> 01:56:46.813
He's our atoner.

01:56:47.669 --> 01:56:48.418
He washed all our sins in His precious blood.

01:56:48.418 --> 01:56:50.513
We don't have to have a goat.

01:56:50.513 --> 01:56:53.619
We don't have to have a sheep.

01:56:53.619 --> 01:57:00.000
We don't have to have a scapegoat go up the side of a mountain.

01:57:00.000 --> 01:57:01.173
We have Jesus.

01:57:04.586 --> 01:57:05.093
And Jesus paid the price for all our sins and all our sickness and all our disease.

01:57:10.489 --> 01:57:26.160
He paid the price for all of us to walk in victory, that we can come to His throne boldly and sit down and say, "Dad, how are you doing today?

01:57:26.160 --> 01:57:28.399
Jesus, how are you doing today?

01:57:28.399 --> 01:57:35.472
" If it wasn't for the blood of Jesus, every one of us would be lost.

01:57:35.472 --> 01:57:56.929
If it wasn't for the blood of Jesus, none of us could walk in divine health.

01:58:07.599 --> 01:58:07.972
I know it was the blood.

01:58:08.719 --> 01:58:10.587
I know it was the blood.

01:58:30.183 --> 01:58:30.571
I know it was the blood for me.

01:58:30.571 --> 01:58:34.592
One day when I was lost, Jesus died on the cross.

01:58:35.154 --> 01:58:37.463
And I know it was the blood for me.

01:58:54.183 --> 01:58:54.446
He's coming back again.

01:58:54.446 --> 01:58:55.760
He's coming back again.

01:58:55.760 --> 01:59:00.009
He's coming back again for me.

01:59:00.009 --> 01:59:02.800
One day when I was lost, Jesus died on the cross.

01:59:19.039 --> 01:59:19.720
And I know it was the blood for me.

01:59:19.720 --> 01:59:25.679
I believe that's the way the words go.

01:59:25.679 --> 01:59:29.940
"Three days and He arose.

01:59:29.940 --> 01:59:35.008
Three days and He arose.

01:59:35.008 --> 01:59:40.120
" I love those old songs.

01:59:49.119 --> 01:59:52.035
He's coming back again for me.

01:59:52.035 --> 01:59:57.650
One day when I was lost, Jesus died on the cross.

01:59:57.650 --> 02:00:00.200
They need to start singing stuff like that again.

02:00:00.200 --> 02:00:02.626
Well, did you get blessed today by it?

02:00:02.626 --> 02:00:05.018
Praise the Lord, I hope you did.

02:00:16.200 --> 02:00:16.540
I was blessed.

02:00:16.540 --> 02:00:17.744
He's coming back again for me.

02:00:17.744 --> 02:00:19.813
I know it was the blood.

02:00:19.813 --> 02:00:23.408
I know it was the blood.

02:00:23.408 --> 02:00:27.090
I know it was the blood for me.

02:00:44.159 --> 02:00:45.039
He shed the blood for me.

02:00:45.039 --> 02:00:47.679
He shed the blood for you.

02:00:47.679 --> 02:00:49.057
Do you believe it?

02:00:49.057 --> 02:00:53.691
One day when I was lost, Jesus died on the cross, and He's coming back again for me.

02:00:53.691 --> 02:00:55.863
I like those old songs; they get you dancing.

02:00:55.863 --> 02:00:58.080
Nancy's coming to our church.

02:00:58.080 --> 02:01:04.630
Nancy Dufresne's coming to the church this next week all for a bunch of days.

02:01:04.630 --> 02:01:06.999
Then Billy Burke, you follow Tennessee.

02:01:24.560 --> 02:01:25.200
The prayer conference is the fifteenth, sixteenth, seventeenth, eighteenth, nineteenth, and twentieth in Branson, Missouri—Sister Billye Brim, her prayer conference.

02:01:42.400 --> 02:01:42.738
And boy, are they going to have a meeting.

02:01:42.738 --> 02:01:49.510
They're going to have special guests there, Lynne Hammond.

02:01:49.520 --> 02:01:52.279
It's going to be wonderful.

02:01:52.279 --> 02:01:54.537
I'm excited about it.

02:01:54.537 --> 02:01:57.720
We're going to go and get in the prayer flow.

02:01:57.720 --> 02:01:59.771
There's a lot of good intercessors.

02:01:59.771 --> 02:02:07.544
They all assemble together, and boy, I tell you what, you can feel the river when they all pray.

02:02:07.544 --> 02:02:11.200
I just love it.

02:02:24.827 --> 02:02:25.102
You learn to cut your teeth on that kind of stuff.

02:02:25.102 --> 02:02:26.660
It's just changed my life.

02:02:26.660 --> 02:02:33.535
Why I am who I am was listening to Sister Lynne and Lucy and Billye and all the greats.

02:02:33.535 --> 02:02:36.179
It's where you learn.

02:02:36.179 --> 02:02:38.380
You've got to learn from the elders.

02:02:38.380 --> 02:02:41.760
And I'm telling you, it'll change your life.

02:02:42.427 --> 02:02:43.760
Don't go Rambo, you know.

02:02:43.760 --> 02:02:45.271
So, glory to God.

02:02:45.271 --> 02:02:47.919
Anybody have any questions or anything before I go?

02:02:47.919 --> 02:02:48.639
Excuse me.

02:02:48.639 --> 02:02:51.314
Do you see any comments?

02:02:51.314 --> 02:02:52.798
Nothing.

02:02:57.529 --> 02:02:57.813
You want to know anything?

02:03:11.009 --> 02:03:11.299
If not, I can't really go into a lot of what it's about today until I talk to my friend.

02:03:11.299 --> 02:03:13.040
But praise the Lord, no.

02:03:25.031 --> 02:03:25.289
"What does Jesus look like?

02:03:25.289 --> 02:03:26.780
What does Jesus look like?

02:03:26.780 --> 02:03:28.693
" Yeah, I'll tell you.

02:03:45.750 --> 02:03:46.000
This is it.

02:03:46.000 --> 02:03:50.159
Every time I think about what I saw, His eyes are pure pools of love.

02:03:55.220 --> 02:03:55.440
You can get lost in His eyes.

02:03:55.440 --> 02:04:00.010
They're the most crystal clear eyes I've ever looked into.

02:04:06.560 --> 02:04:06.800
The way He looks at you is the most yearning and love I can ever describe of anything I've ever seen.

02:04:06.800 --> 02:04:09.580
When He looks at you, He looks right through you.

02:04:09.580 --> 02:04:17.920
When He looks at you, the purity of who He is, it's—when you say love, His eyes are the expression of love.

02:04:17.920 --> 02:04:24.519
They're the most beautiful blue-green looking color I've ever seen.

02:04:24.519 --> 02:04:26.377
But there's no end to them.

02:04:26.377 --> 02:04:30.040
His hair goes real tailored to about right here, but it's tailored.

02:04:30.040 --> 02:04:33.298
It's very manicured and it's a beautiful brown color.

02:04:33.298 --> 02:04:35.386
His beard is perfect.

02:04:35.386 --> 02:04:41.098
His beard is very tailored and perfect.

02:04:57.760 --> 02:04:58.400
It's not long and bushy; it's tailored.

02:04:58.400 --> 02:05:03.840
Everything about Him, His skin tone is an olive.

02:05:03.840 --> 02:05:11.599
It's not white like Brandon; it's more of a brown, like an olive.

02:05:11.599 --> 02:05:13.870
But His beard is a brown; it's not black.

02:05:13.870 --> 02:05:21.376
It's brown like the shade of His hair, but His eyes are a blue, like a green-blue.

02:05:21.376 --> 02:05:26.719
They're the most piercing color of blue I've ever seen, like a beautiful color.

02:05:26.719 --> 02:05:33.440
They were not brown; they looked blue to me.

02:05:39.741 --> 02:05:39.990
And you know what?

02:05:39.990 --> 02:05:43.799
Remember whenever I had the throne experience?

02:05:57.120 --> 02:05:57.792
The eye that came out of the eye was like an all-seeing eye, but it came out and there was fire dancing in the middle of it.

02:05:57.792 --> 02:06:00.624
Fire was moving all inside of the eye.

02:06:00.624 --> 02:06:10.674
It wasn't one fire; it was hundreds of fires burning all inside of the eye because He was a consuming fire.

02:06:19.999 --> 02:06:20.399
The fire was dancing upon fire as I looked into it.

02:06:40.560 --> 02:06:40.830
And it was everything I could do not to wet myself.

02:06:43.988 --> 02:06:50.549
I'm not trying to be funny; I'm just being real with you.

02:06:50.549 --> 02:06:57.920
It was the most fearful thing I've ever seen in my life.

02:07:01.599 --> 02:07:04.137
I literally thought I was going to die.

02:07:11.780 --> 02:07:12.040
The fire was the most consuming fire, and the eyes were fire.

02:07:15.440 --> 02:07:20.373
And His voice was so thunderous that I thought it was going to pierce the inside of me when He spoke.

02:07:32.639 --> 02:07:33.029
And He said, "I am that I am.

02:07:33.029 --> 02:07:34.980
" That's what He said.

02:07:40.680 --> 02:07:42.503
And it was so loud that it shook the very room that I was in: "I am that I am.

02:07:50.871 --> 02:07:51.128
" And it went "woo".

02:07:51.128 --> 02:07:54.959
When He spoke, it went "woo".

02:07:58.340 --> 02:08:02.263
And every one of His words never died; they turned into a seed in front of my face.

02:08:02.263 --> 02:08:05.724
And as He spoke, they all gathered in lines.

02:08:21.473 --> 02:08:21.748
And they all started to sprout like a peanut before me, like spider vines.

02:08:23.633 --> 02:08:26.205
And every word became a word, and it never died.

02:08:29.332 --> 02:08:31.955
And it grew in front of my face as He spoke, and it formed sentences.

02:08:35.805 --> 02:08:38.533
And as the words were coming out, they grew together, and all the words grew together.

02:08:40.700 --> 02:08:42.133
And they went straight down, and the river of it was flowing through His throne.

02:08:42.133 --> 02:08:43.896
It was a river of water.

02:08:52.340 --> 02:08:52.840
And the roots and the words that came forth out of His mouth, they grew into the water and they grew a taproot into the water and they never died.

02:08:52.840 --> 02:08:59.728
Every word that he spoke became a plant, like a growth of something coming out, and it grew.

02:08:59.728 --> 02:09:01.566
His words never die.

02:09:01.566 --> 02:09:03.668
They're always alive.

02:09:03.668 --> 02:09:06.008
They don't return unto him void.

02:09:16.711 --> 02:09:16.888
He doesn't flippantly talk.

02:09:16.888 --> 02:09:29.413
His words become alive in the seed, and they spring forth life as he speaks, and they grow into the water, and the water flows from his throne.

02:09:30.764 --> 02:09:36.336
And there's ankle-deep, waist-deep, and there's over-the-head deep, clear at his throne—the clearest, purest water you've ever seen in your life.

02:09:36.336 --> 02:09:38.016
No pollution, no nothing.

02:09:38.016 --> 02:09:39.822
It's the most beautiful water.

02:09:42.240 --> 02:09:42.440
